# Processed Data

Processed datasets are generated from raw Kaggle data through the preprocessing pipeline.

The processed data includes:

- train.parquet: processed training dataset
- val.parquet: validation dataset
- test.parquet: processed test dataset

Due to large file sizes, processed datasets are not stored in this repository.

To reproduce:
1. Download raw data from Kaggle
2. Run preprocessing notebooks/scripts
3. Generated parquet files will be saved here
